{"tid":2430542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫生打BIONTECH：何栢良稱已為家人預約接種　數據顯示復必泰疫苗安全","createTime":"2021-03-03T04:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T04:20:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b22edf9ff0ab8428c08a6c08244eaf2f299592","tid":2430542,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:18:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578481-20210303.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578481-20210303.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiujC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=74e5e581\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578481-20210303.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a14435b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578481-20210303.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n5個優先群組市民今早9時開始，可以網上預約接種BioNTech的「復必泰」疫苗，港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良說，今早已成功為家人登記預約，他亦積極鼓勵所有家人接種。他說，世界各地有越來越多的成效數據，顯示復必泰疫苗非常安全。<br />\n<br />\n他提到，英國政府最新公布分析成效數據，暫未經同行審批及在醫學期刊發表，但文件已能在網上查閱。當地750萬名70歲或以上人士，在去年12月至上月底接種疫苗，大部分是復必泰，整體成效達到85至90%；80歲以上，成效也有89%。他說，即使流感疫苗，很少70或80歲的成效能超過8成甚至9成。<br />\n<br />\n一名63歲男子上周五接種科興新冠疫苗後，星期日出現急性呼吸困難，自行醫院接治理，同日死亡。何栢良表示，暫時無證據顯示與接種疫苗有關。他說，除了內地，目前已有14個國家廣泛使用科興疫苗，累計有逾1千萬人接種，全球暫時也沒任何證據顯示科興疫苗的安全有擔心。"},{"pid":"e1bcab22af9905bb7fe052440b83f39329808c73","tid":2430542,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fS8Q4k.jpg&amp;h=d97a5cb9&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"d986b9b50d775ec68530bf57e668c131516c6c0b","tid":2430542,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"許樹安呢"},{"pid":"0da0c737297fd7e45b3d122fb8b2b05b2b95b08e","tid":2430542,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d986b9b50d775ec68530bf57e668c131516c6c0b","tid":2430542,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"許樹安呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:20:49.000Z","msg":"唔答, 政治化"},{"pid":"f9c6d6179a39bd3af6c0ea71d76623ab14c9e7d8","tid":2430542,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:20:54.000Z","msg":"五毛pr之後任務就係抹黑外國疫苗，大家唔好中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}